    array['Romanian Deadlift', 'Barbell Squat', 'Front Barbell Squat']::text[],
    'One Leg Barbell Squat Exercise: Muscles Worked, Tips, and How To Do It',
    'Learn how to do the One Leg Barbell Squat exercise, which muscles it works, the equipment you need, and common mistakes to avoid.',
